title: #646 - Jimmy Shubert
description:
Jimmy Shubert, a comedian with more than 30 years experience and actor seen on "The King Of Queens", joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt live in studio.

Jimmy's new special, "Zero Tolerance" will be released on Vimeo on January 15, 2019.
